locality: SW, Province of Toliara (Tulear), c. 35 km north of Tulear (c. 11 km north of Ifaty), near the coast. Over limestone , in spiny scrubland with Didierea madagascariensis and Euphorbias.
Forest with Adansonia rubristipa and Delonix floribunda
N of Toliara, in Forêt de Mikea, ca. 18 road-km W of Vorehe. Deciduous forest on sand. Collected with S. Razafimandimbison, M. Olson & B. Alongi.
Prov. de Tulear: Itambono Corridor between Betioky and Beheloka, 18 km from R.N. 10
Along RN 10 between Tongobory and Betioky
